\begin_inset Formula $|k^{p}a_{k}|<\varepsilon$
\end_inset

.
 Now 
\begin_inset Formula $k^{p}$
\end_inset

 is always positive, so that's 
\begin_inset Formula $k^{p}|a_{k}|<\varepsilon$
\end_inset

.
 We need to show that 
\begin_inset Formula $k^{p}$
\end_inset

